{"fixed_xml":"<ITEM>In denen Thurneysischen Buchläden allhier, seynd dato folgende zwey Bücher zu haben, so in Nancy durch Subscriptiones gedruckt worden. <BIBL><TITLE>Dictionnaire Universel- Francois & Latin, Vulgairement appellé Dictionaire de Trevoux</TITLE>, avec des Remarques d Erudition & de Critique <VOLUME>5. Tom.</VOLUME> <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT> <YEAR>1741</YEAR>; davon die 3. ersten Tom. dato schon zu beziehen sind; das gantze Werck kostet samt der Fracht <PRIZE>fl. 24</PRIZE></BIBL>. <BIBL><TITLE>Dictionaire Oeconomique, continant les moyens d'Augmenter son bien & de conserver sa sante</TITLE>, par <AUTHOR>Mister Noel Chomel</AUTHOR>, Augmente dun Nouveau Supplement de deux Volumes, par <AUTHOR>F. Marset, Doct. en Medecines</AUTHOR>.<FORMAT>avec fig.</FORMAT> <VOLUME>4. Tom.</VOLUME> <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT> <YEAR>1741</YEAR>; davon der erste Tomus dato bey ihnen zu beziehen ist; diß gantze Werck kostet samt der Fracht <PRIZE>fl. 18</PRIZE></BIBL>. So dann sind bey ihnen auch genugsam annoch zu haben: <BIBL><TITLE>Dictionaire Historique & Critique de Mr. Bayle</TITLE>. <VOLUME>4. Tom.</VOLUME> <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT> <PLACE>Amsterd.</PLACE> <YEAR>1740</YEAR>. à <PRIZE>L. 27</PRIZE></BIBL>. <BIBL><TITLE>Corpus Juris Civilis Romani, cum Notis Gotofrest</TITLE> <VOLUME>2. Tom.</VOLUME> <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT> <YEAR>1740</YEAR>. à <PRIZE>fl. 10. 48. xr.</PRIZE></BIBL>. <BIBL><TITLE>Dictionaire Royal, Francois-Allemand-Latin, par le R. P. Fr. Pomey</TITLE> <VOLUME>3. Voll.</VOLUME> <FORMAT>4°.</FORMAT> <YEAR>1741</YEAR>. à <PRIZE>fl. 5. 24. xr.</PRIZE></BIBL></ITEM>","number_of_corrections":13,"explanation":"Fixed the following issues:
1. Replaced corrupted character sequences with correct German characters (√§ → ä in "Buchläden", √ºcher → ücher in "Bücher", √º → ü in "diß")
2. Replaced corrupted √© with é in "appellé"
3. Changed "dien" to "bien" (correct French word)
4. Changed "deur" to "deux" (correct French word)
5. Corrected "2vec" to "avec" in FORMAT tag
6. Replaced corrupted √≤ with ° in "4°" (quarto format)
7. Changed three instances of PRICE tag to PRIZE to match the consistent pattern used elsewhere
8. Replaced corrupted √† with à (French preposition meaning "at")
9. Escaped ampersands (& instead of &) for proper XML formatting
10. Fixed punctuation (removed space before period after "Medecines", added period after "Bayle")
Total: 13 corrections"}

2. Replaced corrupted √© with é in "appellé"
3. Changed "dien" to "bien" (correct French word)
4. Changed "deur" to "deux" (correct French word)
5. Corrected "2vec" to "avec" in FORMAT tag
6. Replaced corrupted √≤ with ° in "4°" (quarto format)

8. Replaced corrupted √† with à (French preposition meaning "at")
9. Escaped ampersands (& instead of &) for proper XML formatting
10. Fixed punctuation (removed space before period after "Medecines", added period after "Bayle")
Total: 13 corrections
